[link: /commands/categories/platform.md] ’Щ@957e4edf2c765c24df452ec2de64603eb988b4d3dd85660cf52d2840bb27e522ЩGTitle: title: kill
Path: Signature
Content:
``> kill {flags} ...rest``
’Щ@cd948f6c42798f47e265b9555cb612ecd381ac764e11af63dca562cb19cd6b8fЩьTitle: title: kill
Path: Flags
Content:
``--force, -f``
: Forcefully kill the process.
``--quiet, -q``
: Won't print anything to the console.
``--signal, -s {int}``
: Signal decimal number to be sent instead of the default 15 (unsupported on Windows).
’Щ@6491a5e4fc39cbd9395ef1fd33283604270d08d3737286c6562df2682ec897deЩkTitle: title: kill
Path: Parameters
Content:
``...rest``
: Process ids of processes that are to be killed.
