’Щ@cdfb12ec1647a66ec0ec0a1eea1f986ffcc942b50fb03aeb784d6b2f3ee5958eЪ(Title: title: kill
Path: Examples
Content:
Kill the pid using the most memory.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> ps | sort-by mem | last | kill $in.pid


```
Force kill a given pid.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> kill --force 12345


```
Send INT signal.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> kill -s 2 12345


```
